    </template>
  </category>

  <category>
    <pattern>^ volleyball ^</pattern>
    <template>
      <set name="sport">Volleyball</set> requires agility and coordination. You can play beach volleyball, indoor matches or just playing normal matches outside
      <br/>Do you want to learn more:
      <br/>- Best Players
      <br/>- Best Teams
